<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.10.4">
<l>pēymu laittalai nañcuṇṭa piḷḷaiyait teḷḷi yārvaṇaṅ kappaṭun tēvaṉai</l>
<l>māya ṉaimatiḷ kōvali ṭaikaḻi mainta ṉaiyaṉṟi yantaṇar cintaiyuḷ</l>
<l>īca ṉaiyilaṅ kumcuṭarc cōtiyai yentai yaiyeṉak keyppiṉil vaippiṉai</l>
<l>kāci ṉaimaṇi yaicceṉṟu nāṭik kaṇṇa maṅkaiyuḷ kaṇṭukoṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having gone searching, I saw for myself in Kaṇṇamaṅkai</l>
<l>The child who ate poison on the tip of the demon’s breast,</l>
<l rend="indent">the deity who is worshiped by the wise,</l>
<l>Māyaṉ, the man of Iṭaikaḻi in walled Kōvalūr, moreover,</l>
<l rend="indent">the lord in the minds of the priests,</l>
<l>The splendor of the shining sun, my father, the cure for me</l>
<l rend="indent">in [times of] weakness, gold, and jewels.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
